kb3.name: kb3_esisso
kb3.structure: CREATE TABLE `kb3_esisso` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL auto_increment, `characterID` int(11) NOT NULL, `keyType` varchar(16) NOT NULL, `refreshToken` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `ownerHash` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `failCount` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `isEnabled` tinyint(1) NOT NULL, `lastKillID` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `lastKillFetchTimestamp` datetime DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) Engine=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci;
